{"tid":1532954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"六月截止到目前共拘捕1117人，死心啦。","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T16:09:26.000Z","uid":107199,"like":17,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"49dd6dc217b561b753b9f42568070cb89cfdaf17","tid":1532954,"uid":107199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"真係死心啦？近排身邊好多朋友都好灰，係場運動睇唔到希望。<br />\n法律無人制裁到警察<br />\n政府繼續漠視民意<br />\n差唔多每日都睇到有義士俾人拉，每次聽到我都好灰好頹<br />\n831直播地鐵站我睇到喊，好心痛，好無力，好痛恨。<br />\n但我唔會死心<br />\n我會繼續同大家行落去<br />\n如果依家放棄我地點對得住俾人拉左既義士？我地點對得住係示威受傷既手足？<br />\n呢幾個月我對自己係香港人身分認同愈黎愈深<br />\n我好自豪有你地每一位出黎既手足<br />\n我希望大家唔好忘記，一個都不能少<br />\n出得嚟既每一位，我都當你地係我家人<br />\n各位一齊行落去，唔好灰心，就算剩返我一個，我都會繼續出黎抗爭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，加油！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f2bdfcdb8797b650fd7e30144b50c76c056aec2b","tid":1532954,"uid":132497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"希望有人幫手統籌<br />\n<br />\n[創舉] 10月1日，香港人要搞個健力士世界紀錄<br />\n<br />\n如果個日全香港人舉唔同國家既國旗，唯獨是無中共垃圾旗，搞個健力士世界紀錄，有無得諗<br />\n<br />\n香港人要入健力士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落佢鬼國面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Record breaking] Oct 1, HongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<br />\n<br />\nIf all the HongKongers carry different countries national flags, except the one of CCP, and break a Guiness World Record, sound good?<br />\n<br />\nHongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLose ChiNazi&rsquo;s face<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532234</a>"},{"pid":"00df4268ae1d54dc1445d6f519abdf3d5ee05af4","tid":1532954,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:47:09.000Z","msg":"200萬人拉左1200人<br />\n死乜野心<br />\n佢地拉得曬200萬先出聲啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513da5fba442c6923f66024da75fc1d9635b66b9","tid":1532954,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"咁你個標題就唔好打&quot;死心啦&quot;屌你,係咁放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333f3cd967eb788fc45ff80df45e0b8bccbd428b","tid":1532954,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"請唔好放負 唔該<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油 <br />\n<br />\n條路好難行 但我地會一直互相扶持行落去"},{"pid":"6f3cfe9ab2152622679c5095476f6fa4a38c329c","tid":1532954,"uid":107199,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"513da5fba442c6923f66024da75fc1d9635b66b9","tid":1532954,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"咁你個標題就唔好打&quot;死心啦&quot;屌你,係咁放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身邊有朋友俾人拉左，的確好重負能量，但個標題都係想大家入黎睇下，唔好放棄"},{"pid":"d0a98843076d76d10aca1a88f7b629d194b903f9","tid":1532954,"uid":249041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:53:53.000Z","msg":"不要放棄呀..如果要放棄 點解要堅持左咁耐先放棄？點面對被捕果1117手足 加油啊！！！"},{"pid":"e7d5f74bbe412825210c2b36132e52474a615a52","tid":1532954,"uid":107199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0a98843076d76d10aca1a88f7b629d194b903f9","tid":1532954,"uid":249041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:53:53.000Z","msg":"不要放棄呀..如果要放棄 點解要堅持左咁耐先放棄？點面對被捕果1117手足 加油啊！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:54:15.000Z","msg":"加油呀手足！！！！"},{"pid":"f3a6c27f3d655fb5b818b43db9484ea3876ad4f2","tid":1532954,"uid":278184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"屌你咪撚標題黨啦<b